metadata.title: Azure AI-102: AI Engineer Associate Practice Quiz
metadata.description: A comprehensive practice quiz for individuals preparing for the Microsoft Azure AI Engineer Associate (AI-102) certification. This quiz covers the key skills measured in the exam, including planning and managing AI solutions, and implementing computer vision, natural language processing, knowledge mining, and document intelligence solutions.
metadata.author: amankumarshrestha
quiz_tags: Plan and manage an Azure AI solution
Implement knowledge mining and document intelligence solutions
